No. 456,

Misc.

Fredericks v. United States. Bernard A. Golding for petitioner. Solicitor General Sobeloff, Assistant Attorney General Olney, Beatrice Rosenberg and Robert G. Maysack for the United States.

C. A. 5th Cir. Certiorari denied.
